snippet.title: Amber Heard back in Aquaman 2 and Beyond
snippet.description:
#AmberHeard #Aquaman #JusticeLeague

Many were hoping the role of Mera would be recast in Aquaman 2, but according to a new repoort from Mikey Sutton, they are out of luck. Not only will she be back for that, she may even back for Justice League 2 and beyond.

Check out Mikey Sutton's Geekosity:
https://www.geekositymag.com

Earlier report from Pop Culture Minefield:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i2PAw8Tru90
